data_site <- "http://tiny.cc/dcf/2014-Q4-Trips-History-Data-Small.rds"
Trips <- readRDS(gzcon(url(data_site)))

1

ggplot(Trips, aes(x = sdate)) + geom_density()

2

Trips%>%
 mutate(time_of_day =
           lubridate::hour(sdate) +
           lubridate::minute(sdate)/60) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = time_of_day)) + geom_density()

3

data_trips <- Trips %>%
  mutate(time_of_day =
           lubridate::hour(sdate) +
           lubridate::minute(sdate)/60) %>%
  mutate(day_of_week =
           lubridate::wday(sdate))
ggplot(data_trips,aes(x = time_of_day)) + geom_density() + facet_wrap(~ day_of_week)

4

Trips%>%
  mutate(time_of_day =
           lubridate::hour(sdate) +
           lubridate::minute(sdate)/60) %>%
  mutate(day_of_week =
           lubridate::wday(sdate)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = time_of_day)) + geom_density(aes(fill = client), alpha = .3) + facet_wrap(~ day_of_week)

5

Trips%>%
  mutate(time_of_day =
           lubridate::hour(sdate) +
           lubridate::minute(sdate)/60) %>%
  mutate(day_of_week =
           lubridate::wday(sdate)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = time_of_day)) + geom_density(aes(fill = client), alpha = .3, position = position_stack()) + facet_wrap(~ day_of_week)
